take four to five cups of water in deep sauce pan bring in to boil over medium flame when it starts boiling add 3/4 cup penne pasta and half teaspoon salt it will take around 10 to
12 min to cook pasta take one pasta in a fork and bite it to check if it is cooked or not now transfer cooked pasta into a large colander and drain excess water while pasta is 
cooking , heat 1/2 teaspoon oil in a pan or kadai over high flame add 1/4 cup of chopped carrot , 1.4 cup chopped green capsicum , 1/4 cup chopped red capsicum , 1/4 cup chopped
broccoli and salt
